title.narrative: Second Private Sector and Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises Development Program - Subprogram 2

description.narrative: Subprogram 2 of the Second Private Sector and Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises Development Program (PSME2) and the TA loan support the government's strategy to develop and promote small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and undertake SME trade-related reforms to help achieve sustained and inclusive economic growth-a strategy embedded in the Seventh National Socio-Economic Development Plan (NSEDP7), 2011-2015.
